Malice:

He could not believe what he was hearing.  He simply couldn&#39;t.  he reached out and held her close to him.

&quot;No Wolfblade!  Don&#39;t leave me!  It was wrong of me to think this would work out, I was a fool.  Don&#39;t go, I could not live without you.&quot;

He struggled to his feet, in actual physical pain.  He pulled her up with him, pain and sorrow etched into his faceplates. 

&quot;I will handle this, please do not leave me.  It&#39;s my turn to make a hard decision.  Stay with me, and when this is over, I&#39;ll take you to someplace we can live together happily.&quot;

